# Geo Risk Intelligence Pipeline

## Scope
- Phase 1: Fabric-first Bronze → Silver → Gold; batch only (no streaming).
- Historical window: last 30 days of event_ts only.
- Environments: dev | test | prod via config/environments.yaml + Fabric Variable Library.
- Dual Gold: gold_fraud_signals, gold_customer_features, gold_geo_traffic_daily.

## Code simplicity
- Mirror databricks_vic_traffic numbered notebooks; Config + one loader class per layer.
- No frameworks; if logic is used once, keep it in that notebook.

## Medallion
- Bronze: raw events + raw IPstack JSON (never drop response_json).
- Silver: silver_ip_dim cache + silver_events_enriched.
- Gold: use event_ts for time logic, not api_called_at.

## Secrets
- IPSTACK_ACCESS_KEY via Variable Library or .env — never commit keys.
